original_title: Gustav Holst: The Planets - Edward Gardner and the National Youth Orchestra
overview: Edward Gardner leads the National Youth Orchestra of Great Britain and the CBSO Youth Chorus in a performance of Gustav Holst's The Planets with Colin Matthews' supplementary piece "Pluto, The Renewer."  Recorded live at the Royal Albert Hall on August 6th 2016 as part of BBC Prom 29.
title: Gustav Holst: The Planets - Edward Gardner and the National Youth Orchestra
